        <h1 class="article-title">Chinese mental health services falling short: report</h1>
        <div class="article-type">
          
          <span class="article-type-item">China Plus/Xinhua</span>
          <span class="article-type-item article-type-item-time">Published: 2019-02-25 19:22:56</span>
